title: Shane And Shane Discography 1998-2014 (26 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SHANE AND SHANE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 26 releases...

 * 1998 - Rocks Wont Cry
 * 2002 - Psalms
 * 2003 - Carry Away
 * 2004 - Clean
 * 2004 - Upstairs
 * 2005 - An Evening With
 * 2006 - Bluegrass Sampler
 * 2007 - Pages
 * 2008 - Glory In The Highest - A Christmas Record
 * 2009 - Everything Is Different
 * 2009 - We Love You Jesus EP
 * 2010 - Dare 2 Share - Unending Worship
 * 2010 - Pages, Special Edition
 * 2011 - The One You Need
 * 2013 - Bring Your Nothing
 * 2014 - A Worship Initiative Christmas
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 1
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 2
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 3
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 4
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 5
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 6
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 7
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 8
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 9
 * 2014 - The Worship Initiative, Vol 10

Shane And Shane is a Texas-based, Christian band known for acoustic praise and worship music. The band consists of Shane Barnard (vocals, acoustic guitar) and Shane Everett (vocals). They are often joined by their drummer and manager, Joey Parish.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - December 2014
